title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: In Dreams
description: Steven's dreams start broadcasting onto his bedroom TV.

title: El regreso de Xingo
description: Cuando Ben debe divertirse solo durante la merecida siesta de Max, se topa con un juego de Xingo y decide convertirse en OE-Shock Rock para encenderlo. Pero cuando Xingo recibe demasiada carga, salta al mundo real, y nuestro héroe debe quedar frente a frente con su personaje animado favorito.

title: Steven Universe Future - Catch Up Trailer
description: Catch up on everything going on with Steven and the gems in Steven Universe Future so far!  This trailer covers the most important events of the first ten episodes of Steven Universe Future.

title: Ciudad de bichos
description: Craig descubre un montón de insectos bajo una roca y decide construirles una ciudad.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Scratch Pack
description: Axel and the team must run damage control after a loose spark of Minergy accidentally turns Zoe's old toys - a set of cute squishy kittens - into a pack of snarling beasts.

title: Aspirations
description: The Gangreen Gang is actually committing brilliant crimes. But behind every great gang, there has to be a great woman.

title: Too Cool
description: Puppycorn needs a lesson in how to be cool. The gang is more than happy to teach him, until his coolness unexpectedly freezes the whole kingdom.

title: A Rocky Start
description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

title: True Kinda Love Official Music Video
description: : The official music video for "True Kinda Love" by Estelle feat. Zach Callison from Steven Universe The Movie.

title: Secret of the Unicorn
description: A crying unicorn appears at the Cats' Lair and weepily tells the ThunderCats that all of her unicorn friends have been captured! Tygra thinks he's just the unicorn expert to help the last of the unicorns, he just needs her to stop sobbing long enough to tell him who took her friends. Easier said than done.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Turning the Tables
description: Craig dines at the restaurant where his older brother works and orders up a plate of REVENGE... and lots of breadsticks.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: #AllyCat Part 2
description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

title: Orangusnake Begins
description: Mao Mao goads Orangusnake and the Sky Pirates into becoming truly terrible villains worthy of a legendary hero such as himself.

title: The Belly of the Beast
description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

title: Churro Kings
description: When Vic & Val start making good money from selling churros at the taco stand, their lust for stuff makes them do dirty tricks to take out their competition.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Half-Sies
description: During a trip to the Lake of the Ozarks, Ben and Gwen squabble over Ben's unnecessary "half-birthday" celebration, but when Max gets word of a suspicious rockslide nearby, the cousins must put aside their differences if they are to rescue the trapped miners and uncover who is behind the manmade catastrophe before it's too late: the Bugg Brothers.

title: Savage Axel
description: Bearbarian helps Axel get in touch with his wild side as Orangutank "liberates" nature from an apartment building - tossing potted plants of all sizes out the window and onto innocent bystanders below!

title: El Vientre del Monstruo
description: Para reparar el Land-Bounty, el ninja debe recuperar un componente crítico del motor que ha sido tragado por un escarabajo gigante.

title: West in Pieces
description: It's the old west and Mojo the Kid has robbed the first bank ever and forced the sheriff out of town and it is up to the Steamypuff Girls to save the day at a high-noon showdown.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Greatest Lake
description: While visiting Lake Erie, a relaxing day at the beach gets all washed up when Ben, Gwen and Grandpa Max come face-to-face with Hex, and his summer intern, Kevin!

title: The Fly
description: Apple and Onion must rid their apartment of a fly or face eviction.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Record Book
description: Starfire wants a world record, so she decides to grow her fingernails.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: Kelsey the Author
description: Craig and Stacks help Kelsey become a real author turning her story into a book!

title: I See a Funny Cartoon in Your Future/Octi-Gone
description: I See a Funny Cartoon In Your Future: The girls have the rare task of fighting a medium who is committing petty thefts./Octi-gone: When Bubbles finds a single leg of Octi's, she sets out to find out who took her toy and what they want from her.

title: Roughing It Up/What's the Big Idea
description: Roughing It Up: The girls and the Professor set out on an old-fashioned vacation to the Townsville Swamp. Trouble is, Fuzzy and his nephews are there, too./What's the Big Idea: 20 story high Powerpuff Girls spell disaster for Townsville when they delicately try to stop Mojo from taking over.

title: Bounty Ball
description: While Gwen listens to a lecture on the Transcontinental Railroad, Ben sneaks away to the gift shop. But once the Bounty Hunters appear and corner our hero, Gwen must relay the information she learned on the train and use it to their advantage to help Ben escape.

title: Xingo's Back
description: Left to entertain himself as Max takes a much deserved nap, Ben stumbles upon a Xingo arcade game and goes OE-Shock Rock to power it up, but when it receives too much juice, Xingo leaps out into the real world and our hero must go toe-to-toe with his favorite cartoon character.

title: That's Not My Baby/Simian Says
description: That's Not My Baby!: The girls save a baby from a monster attacking Townsville but can't find the mother. Can these three superheroes manage to take care of one little baby?/Simian Says: When the Narrator is mysteriously bound and gagged, Mojo Jojo takes over his job, ordering the girls to steal for him all around Townsville.

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Apple and Onion have to defend the music store from instrument theft to get a key to the store.

title: Deep Creek Salvage
description: The Trio finds gold in the muddy depths of the Creek so Craig builds a rig to recover it.

title: Bug City
description: Craig discovers a bunch of bugs under a rock and decides to build them a city.

title: Buscando a Jessica
description: Jessica se adentra en un Arroyo desconocido, iy Craig debe encontrarla antes de que su madre se dé cuenta!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: #AllyCat Part 1
description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

title: Del Otro Lado de la Mesa
description: Craig almuerza en el restaurante donde trabaja su hermano mayor y pide un plato de VENGANZA… y muchos palitos de pan.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: A Media
description: Durante un viaje al Lago de los Ozarks, Ben y Gwen discuten sobre la innecesaria celebración de "medio cumpleaños" de Ben. Pero cuando Max se entera de un sospechoso desprendimiento de rocas cercano, los primos deben dejar de lado sus diferencias si quieren rescatar a los mineros atrapados y revelar quién está detrás de la catástrofe producida por el hombre antes de que sea demasiado tarde: los hermanos Bugg.

title: Baku-Gear/Bakugan Rock!
description: Baku-Gear: The Awesome Brawlers are excited over their discovery of Baku-Gear, and want to get some footage of it in action. While they're filming, an underclassman named Trey challenges Dan to battle. Who will emerge victorious in the impromptu battle?/Bakugan Rock!: Baku-gear has shown up twice for Dan and Drago and it's starting to eat away at the other awesome brawlers. It's time they take it into their own hands. When Lia and Wynton go up against the rockin' new brawlers in town, they show Dan and Drago that they are not the only one who can summon this cool new tool!

title: A Licking Time Bomb
description: Owen and Noah unwittingly become cookie moguls and must hide the secret ingredient, which is Owen's spit from licking the sprinkles off the cookies.

title: Jessica's Trail
description: Jessica wanders into an unfamiliar creek, leaving Craig to find her before his Mom notices!

title: Snow Way Out
description: Owen wants everyone to love his new snowsuit and envy him, but it's just not working out that way.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Mud on the Run
description: Ben gets a tough lesson on knowing his limits when he competes in a grueling obstacle race, made even worse by the Weatherheads!

title: Bismuth Casual
description: Pearl invites Bismuth to the roller rink for a lesson on how to forge human relationships.

title: From Badge to Worse

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Driller
description: Panthro is getting a little fed up with having to fix things around the Cats' Lair constantly, which is unfortunate because the ThunderCats are about to be attacked by an unstoppable drilling robot, and he's gonna break everything!

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Cazarecompensas
description: Mientras Gwen escucha una conferencia sobre el Ferrocarril Transcontinental, Ben se escapa en secreto a la tienda de regalos. Pero una vez que los Cazarrecompensas aparecen y acorralan a nuestro héroe, Gwen debe transmitir la información que aprendió en el tren y utilizarla para ayudar a Ben a escapar.

title: Sugar Berry Fever
description: Mao Mao tries to hide his love of cobbler.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Un Comienzo Dificil
description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

title: All Up in Your Drill
description: Duncan stages a small coup to oust Courtney as their official class firefighter so that he can wear the shiny firefighter helmet - until he smells smoke in the classroom and begs her to take her job back.

title: Rescate en el Arroyo Profundo
description: El trío encuentra oro en las fangosas profundidades del Arroyo, por lo que Craig construye un equipo para recuperarlo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Mysterious Boy/A New Power
description: The Mysterious Boy: After stopping Tiko's rampage, the Awesome Brawlers have become world-famous heroes and Bakugan-mania sweeps the globe. With the Bakugan boom, brawling has been reinvented as a sporting game. In celebration of the Awesome Brawlers efforts, a tournament is being held in their honor. But the battles are quickly cut short when a rogue brawler and his golden Bakugan crash the event./A New Power: A Rogue brawler, Agit and his golden Bakugan have crashed the Awesome Brawlers party. Who is this brawler? How can he control a Golden Bakugan? Only one way to find out - Bakugan Brawl! Dan and Drago go head to head with the outsides to get to the bottom of it. Outmatched by their opponent, Dan and Drago get a little help from a new powerful weapon - Baku-Gear.

title: Kelsey la autora
description: iCraig y Stacks ayudan a Kelsey a convertirse en una verdadera autora al convertir su historia en un libro!

title: Walk Away
description: After the T-Car is destroyed in a fight, the Titans go to a used car lot to find another vehicle.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.

title: Toys Will Be Toys
description: Courtney becomes a toy tester but forgets that the most important thing is to have fun.
